Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落 50年前为了抢夺四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设计让犬夜叉与桔梗自相残杀的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他收集起散落的四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今妖力越来越强了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师因奈落之诅咒 在右手留下了一个风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天 会将自己吞噬的风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前 弥勒必须打倒奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚则是亲眼看着父亲与除妖师的同伴们被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这皆因奈落卑鄙地操纵了她的弟弟琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不弄脏自己双手的卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天 我们一定要消灭他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐之舞与神无之镜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说那个叫神乐的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是从奈落身上生出来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得应该有这个可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫奈落的应该是男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人怎么可能生出女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落本来就是妖怪聚集而成的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把她想像成是分裂出来的如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.43,0:04:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说是奈落本人变的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们的事也太不了解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过不管她是什么样的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要想起她是奈落的一部分我就敬谢不敏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们又不是在交往…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点吧 弥勒一族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 要产生风太容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟奈落有同样气味的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人背后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实有跟奈落一样的蜘蛛形状的烧伤痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 你们不觉得奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫神乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是女人但妖力不比寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能创造出这样的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他以前从来没有这样做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是他之前不这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是现在才有能力这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落又有了新的能力是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏你承受了铁碎牙的那一击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总算能够看清楚那把刀的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在再去一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经派出了你的姐姐 神无了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 那野丫头跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然敢反抗油老爷的公子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到小春那个丫头之后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先给我打断她的手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是小春没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才想问你们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来应该只是普通的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女的不是小春
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮 带她回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点乖乖就范
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你敢不从的话 别怪我们手下不留情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 那个女孩危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是老大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少…少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起我们错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.37,0:08:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷 您振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷的脸被打歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙搞什么鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请…请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是来追你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是弥勒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人 我好想你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我们在哪里见过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是小春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你是那时的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们3年没见了 弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 你变得我都不认识了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真叫人怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女孩子是弥勒的朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得好像根本就是朋友以上的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在战争中失去了父母跟兄弟姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被油老爷捡回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从早到晚有做不完的苦工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又饿又累的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都以泪洗面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时侯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有到村子里来驱邪的弥勒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我最温柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫做小春对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年几岁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11岁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春 我问你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以为我生小孩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…为何你们要后退？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然连小孩子都不放过！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禽兽！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我实在是太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要负责哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我还没有碰过小春分毫…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她那时还只是孩子嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时 弥勒大人很快就离开村子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天他会回来接我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直是这么相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.22,0:10:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是最近油老爷的公子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时常用很恶心的眼神看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他终于想强行将我占有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就逃了出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用木柴打他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁他不能动的时侯逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人 请您带我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经无处可去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:10:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以为弥勒大人生小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明年纪比我还小…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然战国时代的女孩子很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒 你应该知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能带那个女孩一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我们也不能把她留在这不管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少在帮她找到一个安全的栖身之所前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须留在她身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家也是愿意给你生小孩的人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我对遇到的每个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会提出这样的要求的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就没对我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 珊瑚 你愿意为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人是你的初恋情人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没有忘记过他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信一定能再重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要这么想 不管多苦我都能忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初恋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在觉得好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算死了也没有任何的遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那真是个可怜的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您能收留她在这个村子里吗 村长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把她交给我吧 法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会给大家添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.68,0:13:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们在一起很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就死了心留在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样对你比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经跟村长商量过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春 你过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人 我们好不容易再见面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却马上又要分开了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要谅解我 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是遇到战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:14:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知能否保护你的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在追寻的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个很可怕的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要跟你分开我也很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那是在说服那女孩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去像打情骂俏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真受不了他 拖泥带水的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样只会让小春对他更留恋嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是我想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 你从刚才开始就好像有点紧张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.91,0:14:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请至少让我跟您在相处一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然小春都这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何呢 就留下来过夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 我再久留的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会让小春更添相思之苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今晚就再跟她倾述一下离别之情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且小春对这座村庄还很陌生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不小心让小春怀了宝宝的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春会怀念我的面容一辈子的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心让小春怀宝宝？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒 那是什么意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用再解释了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝还是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最怕的就是眼泪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我们明天天亮才离开村子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 明天不能再哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到没
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热水的温度可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会为了弥勒大人施展我全部手艺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全心全意做一顿晚餐的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些炖菜真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.77,0:17:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春真是坚强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了讨弥勒法师的欢心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很努力地做了料理哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得小春为我们做这顿晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕没有办法趁热吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并没有妖怪的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我们出去看看再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让他们离开村子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他们全杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.09,0:17:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是村里的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像被什么控制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.47,0:18:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 他们都是普通人类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人数好像很多 我也去帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？小春
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪突然出现 把村长大人他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村长大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是妖怪干的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春 你有看到那是什么样的妖怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我只稍微看到了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉说并没有闻到妖怪的气味啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.97,0:20:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 你要不要紧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女孩是妖怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春 你干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂 给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:20:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 要手下留情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些村民被人控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要伤害到他们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去没完没了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你们也太天真了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气杀光不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们再也爬不起来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 要是你们真能把对他们下手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.81,0:21:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始就该动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你控制这些村民的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有灵魂的人跟死人也没什么两样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有灵魂？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.12,0:21:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在那个叫戈薇的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂也已经被吸走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说 这里还有另外一个妖怪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.73,0:21:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 拔出铁碎牙吧 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次可不会像上次那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怕了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒 你快回到戈薇他们那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 那你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.65,0:22:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要在这解决这个臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风刃之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去 弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.60,0:22:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在去也来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.61,0:22:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 云母
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.13,0:22:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.83,0:23:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒大人 我好怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别怕 已经不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！你想对戈薇怎么样！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:43.26,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 2,0:23:31.64,0:23:37.17,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们 在生命的旅程中{\fad(400,0)}
Dialogue: 2,0:23:37.67,0:23:43.17,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}渐渐地 失去所有
Dialogue: 2,0:23:43.62,0:23:48.99,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我仍坚信着 追逐着光明
Dialogue: 2,0:23:49.62,0:23:56.17,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在与你 一同出发{\fad(0,1050)}
Dialogue: 2,0:24:01.02,0:24:06.22,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如今在那深深的丛林中
